      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just hard to see the point of any of this lately. like, we're just tiny specks on a rock that's eventually going to be swallowed by the sun, and then even the sun dies. everything we do, every struggle, every feeling... it just evaporates. it feels pretty pointless when you really look at the scale of it all.",
